            <td>Call recording</td>
            <td>$1,200/seat/year</td>
            <td>Enterprise teams (10+ reps) needing deep coaching analytics and CRM integration</td>
            <td>You have fewer than 10 reps or a tight budget</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Fathom <span class="tag-best">Top pick SMB</span></td>
            <td>Call recording</td>
            <td>Free / $20/seat Team</td>
            <td>Small teams (1 to 5 reps) needing clean summaries and follow-up drafts</td>
            <td>You need enterprise-grade coaching analytics</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Granola</td>
            <td>Meeting notes</td>
            <td>$10/seat/mo</td>
